OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with bright spells
OL,6,Ffor a time this morning in eastern
OL,7,Fareas, but cloud and patchy rain in
OL,8,Fthe west spreads to most places by
OL,9,Fmidday. Sunny spells and isolated
OL,10,Fblustery showers follow with
OL,11,Fwidespread gusty winds developing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWidely dry and bright this
OL,14,Fevening, although still windy at
OL,15,Ftimes. Cloud thickening overnight with
OL,16,Fscattered showers pushing in from the
OL,17,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
