OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fdeveloping with occasional showers
OL,7,Fbecoming less widespread during the
OL,8,Fday. Windy and feeling rather cool
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FGenerally dry with plenty of fine,
OL,13,Fbright weather expected. Winds easing
OL,14,Fby Sunday and remaining fairly light
OL,15,Fon Monday and Tuesday. Turning
OL,16,Fslightly warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
